        <script language=javascript>
function cshow(id)
{
var obj=document.getElementById(id);
if (obj.style.display=="none")
 {obj.style.display="";}
else
 {obj.style.display="none";}
}
function startlist(root)
{  
	//alert(root.getElementsByTagName("li"));
  var objSon = new Array();
  var objSon = root.getElementsByTagName("li") ;
  for(var i=0;i<=objSon.length-1;i++)
    {
          if(objSon[i].lastChild.nodeName.toLowerCase()=="ul")
	        { 
			  objSon[i].onmouseover=function(){  this.lastChild.style.display='block'; $(this).addClass("aulli1on");}
	          objSon[i].onmouseout=function(){  this.lastChild.style.display='none'; $(this).removeClass("aulli1on"); }
			  //startlist(objSon[i].lastChild);
			}
	}
}

 $(".aulli1").each(function(){
		$(this).hover(
			function(){
				$(this).find(".aliul1").show();
				$(this).addClass("aulli1on");
				},
			function(){
				$(this).find(".aliul1").hide();
				$(this).removeClass("aulli1on");
				}
	    );					
});
</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
$(function(){
	$(".like_sold .like").click(function(){
		var _this = this;
		$.ajax({
		   type: "GET",
		   url: "/index.php?action=add_favorite",
		   data: {pid:$(this).attr('data_id'),ajax:1},
		   dataType: "json",
		   success: function(res){
			 if(res.status)
			 {
				 var old_num = $(_this).text();
				 old_num = old_num.replace("Like(","");
				 old_num = old_num.replace(")","");
				 old_num = parseInt(old_num);
				 old_num = old_num+1;
				 $(_this).text("Like("+old_num+")");
				 $(_this).tip(res.msg, 15, 0, 2000);
			 }
			 else
			 {
				 $(_this).tip(res.msg, 15, 0, 2000);
			 }
		   }
		});
	});
});
function createAjaxLoading()
{
    $('<div/>').appendTo(document.body).addClass('ajax_loading');
}
function removeAjaxLoading()
{
    $('.ajax_loading').remove();
}
</script></div>

</style><script type="text/javascript" src="/skin/default/pic/jq.puzz.js"></script>

<script type="text/javascript">

$(function(){

	$('.quickaddtocart').each(function(){

		$(this).click(function(){

			var _this = $(this);	

			var _parent = $(this).parent().parent();	

			var _quickbox = _parent.find('.quickcart_box');

			if(_quickbox.html()=='')

			{

				_quickbox.show();

				_quickbox.css('position','absolute');

				_quickbox.html('Loading...');

				var size = _this.attr('data');

				result =  eval("("+size+")");

				var carthtml = '<div class="quickcart">   <form>   <input name="id" type="hidden" value="'+_this.attr('pid')+'" />   <input name="quickaddtocart" type="hidden" value="1" />   <ul>';

				carthtml +='        <li>            <div class="property_name">Size : <input name="key0" type="hidden" value="Size" /></div>            <div class="property_value"><select id="style0" name="style0" onchange="quickcartsizechange(this,'+_this.attr('stock')+');"><option value="">Select Size</option>';

                                var total_count = 0;

				for(var key in result)

				{

					result[key] = parseInt(result[key]);	

				    if(result[key]>0)

					{

                                            total_count++;

						if(key=='os')

							size = "one size";

						else

							size = key ;

						carthtml += '<option value="'+size+'" stock="'+result[key]+'">'+size+'</option>';

					}

				}

				carthtml += '</select></div>        </li>';

				carthtml +='        <li>            <div class="property_name">Qty :</div>            <div class="property_value"><input name="num" value="1" /></div>        </li>';

				carthtml +='        <li>            <div class="property_name">Stock :</div>            <div class="property_value"><span class="stock">All '+_this.attr('stock')+' Pcs</span></div>        </li>';

				carthtml +='<li>            <input type="button" value="Submit" class="submit_btn" />            <input type="button" value="Cancel" class="cancel_btn" />        </li>   </ul>   </form></div>';

				_quickbox.html(carthtml);

				_quickbox.css('position','relative');

                                if(total_count==1)

                                {

                                    _quickbox.find('#style0').val(_quickbox.find('#style0').find('option').eq(1).attr('value'));

                                    _quickbox.find('#style0').change();

                                }

			}

			else

			{

				_quickbox.show();

		    }

		});

	});

   $('.quickcart input.submit_btn').live('click',function(){

		var is_submit = true;

		var _this = $(this);

		$(this).parent().parent().parent().find('select').each(function(){

			if(!$(this).val())

			{

				$(this).tip("Please Select " +  $(this).parent().siblings('.property_name').find('input').val(), 15, 0, 2000); 

				is_submit = false;

				return;

			}

		});	

		if(!is_submit)

		{

			return;

		}

		$.ajax({

		   type: "POST",

		   url: "/quickcart.php",

		   data: $(this).parent().parent().parent().serialize(),

		   dataType: "json",

		   success: function(res){

			   if(res.status)

			   {

				   $('#_ajax_div_items').html(res.totalnum);

				   $('._ajax_div_items').html(res.totalnum);

				   _this.tip(res.msg, 15, -1, 2000); 
                   timeId = setTimeout(function() {
						_this.parent().parent().parent().parent().parent().hide();
					}, 3000);	
				var quickaddtocart_obj = _this.parent().parent().parent().parent().parent().parent().find('.quickaddtocart');
				var input_num_obj = _this.parent().parent().find('input[name="num"]');
				ga('ec:addProduct', {      
				   'id': quickaddtocart_obj.attr('data_itemno'),					// SKU   
				   'name': quickaddtocart_obj.attr('data_name'),	// 
				   'category': quickaddtocart_obj.attr('ga_categorys'),				// 
				   'brand': 'DL',						// 
				   'price': quickaddtocart_obj.attr('data_price'),				//   
				   'quantity': input_num_obj.val() ? input_num_obj.val():1,				//   
				   'variant':res.variant
				   });   
				ga('ec:setAction', 'add');   
				ga('send', 'event', 'UX', 'click', 'add to cart');     // Send data using an event.
                
			   }

			   else

			   {

				   _this.tip(res.msg, 15, -1, 2000); 

			   }			   

		   }

		}); 

   });

   $('.favorite_btn').live('click',function(){

		var _this = $(this);

		$.ajax({

		   type: "POST",

		   url: "/quickcart.php",

		   data: {quickaddtofavorite:1,id:_this.attr('pid')},

		   dataType: "json",

		   success: function(res){

			   if(res.status)

			   {

				   _this.tip(res.msg, 15, 0, 2000); 

			   }

			   else

			   {

				   _this.tip(res.msg, 15, 0, 2000); 

			   }			   

		   }

		}); 

   });

   $('.quickcart input.cancel_btn').live('click',function(){$(this).parent().parent().parent().parent().parent().hide();});

});

function quickcartsizechange(obj,allstock)

{

	if($(obj).val())

	{

		size = $(obj).val() ;

		stock = $(obj).find('option:selected').attr('stock');

		$(obj).parent().parent().parent().find('.stock').html($(obj).val()+' : '+stock+' Pcs');

	}

	else

	{

		$(obj).parent().parent().parent().find('.stock').html('All '+allstock+' Pcs');

	}

}

</script>

    $('ul.products li').not('.other').hover(

		function(){

<script>
        $(window).scroll(function() {
            if ($(this).scrollTop() >= 30) {
                $('#top_float').show();
            } else {
                $('#top_float').hide();
            }
        });

        <script language=javascript>
function cshow(id)
{
var obj=document.getElementById(id);
if (obj.style.display=="none")
 {obj.style.display="";}
else
 {obj.style.display="none";}
}
function startlist(root)
{  
	//alert(root.getElementsByTagName("li"));
  var objSon = new Array();
  var objSon = root.getElementsByTagName("li") ;
  for(var i=0;i<=objSon.length-1;i++)
    {
          if(objSon[i].lastChild.nodeName.toLowerCase()=="ul")
	        { 
			  objSon[i].onmouseover=function(){  this.lastChild.style.display='block'; $(this).addClass("aulli1on");}
	          objSon[i].onmouseout=function(){  this.lastChild.style.display='none'; $(this).removeClass("aulli1on"); }
			  //startlist(objSon[i].lastChild);
			}
	}
}

 $(".aulli1").each(function(){
		$(this).hover(
			function(){
				$(this).find(".aliul1").show();
				$(this).addClass("aulli1on");
				},
			function(){
				$(this).find(".aliul1").hide();
				$(this).removeClass("aulli1on");
				}
	    );					
});
</script>

        <script language="javascript">
        //startlist(document.getElementById("nav_class_heng"));

<script type="text/javascript">
$(function(){
	$(".like_sold .like").click(function(){
		var _this = this;
		$.ajax({
		   type: "GET",
		   url: "/index.php?action=add_favorite",
		   data: {pid:$(this).attr('data_id'),ajax:1},
		   dataType: "json",
		   success: function(res){
			 if(res.status)
			 {
				 var old_num = $(_this).text();
				 old_num = old_num.replace("Like(","");
				 old_num = old_num.replace(")","");
				 old_num = parseInt(old_num);
				 old_num = old_num+1;
				 $(_this).text("Like("+old_num+")");
				 $(_this).tip(res.msg, 15, 0, 2000);
			 }
			 else
			 {
				 $(_this).tip(res.msg, 15, 0, 2000);
			 }
		   }
		});
	});
});
function createAjaxLoading()
{
    $('<div/>').appendTo(document.body).addClass('ajax_loading');
}
function removeAjaxLoading()
{
    $('.ajax_loading').remove();
}
</script></div>

.zoom2 { border:1px #A6A6A6 solid}

</style><script type="text/javascript" src="/skin/default/pic/jq.puzz.js"></script>

<script type="text/javascript">

$(function(){

	$('.quickaddtocart').each(function(){

		$(this).click(function(){

			var _this = $(this);	

			var _parent = $(this).parent().parent();	

			var _quickbox = _parent.find('.quickcart_box');

			if(_quickbox.html()=='')

			{

				_quickbox.show();

				_quickbox.css('position','absolute');

				_quickbox.html('Loading...');

				var size = _this.attr('data');

				result =  eval("("+size+")");

				var carthtml = '<div class="quickcart">   <form>   <input name="id" type="hidden" value="'+_this.attr('pid')+'" />   <input name="quickaddtocart" type="hidden" value="1" />   <ul>';

				carthtml +='        <li>            <div class="property_name">Size : <input name="key0" type="hidden" value="Size" /></div>            <div class="property_value"><select id="style0" name="style0" onchange="quickcartsizechange(this,'+_this.attr('stock')+');"><option value="">Select Size</option>';

                                var total_count = 0;

				for(var key in result)

				{

					result[key] = parseInt(result[key]);	

				    if(result[key]>0)

					{

                                            total_count++;

						if(key=='os')

							size = "one size";

						else

							size = key ;

						carthtml += '<option value="'+size+'" stock="'+result[key]+'">'+size+'</option>';

					}

				}

				carthtml += '</select></div>        </li>';

				carthtml +='        <li>            <div class="property_name">Qty :</div>            <div class="property_value"><input name="num" value="1" /></div>        </li>';

				carthtml +='        <li>            <div class="property_name">Stock :</div>            <div class="property_value"><span class="stock">All '+_this.attr('stock')+' Pcs</span></div>        </li>';

				carthtml +='<li>            <input type="button" value="Submit" class="submit_btn" />            <input type="button" value="Cancel" class="cancel_btn" />        </li>   </ul>   </form></div>';

				_quickbox.html(carthtml);

				_quickbox.css('position','relative');

                                if(total_count==1)

                                {

                                    _quickbox.find('#style0').val(_quickbox.find('#style0').find('option').eq(1).attr('value'));

                                    _quickbox.find('#style0').change();

                                }

			}

			else

			{

				_quickbox.show();

		    }

		});

	});

   $('.quickcart input.submit_btn').live('click',function(){

		var is_submit = true;

		var _this = $(this);

		$(this).parent().parent().parent().find('select').each(function(){

			if(!$(this).val())

			{

				$(this).tip("Please Select " +  $(this).parent().siblings('.property_name').find('input').val(), 15, 0, 2000); 

				is_submit = false;

				return;

			}

		});	

		if(!is_submit)

		{

			return;

		}

		$.ajax({

		   type: "POST",

		   url: "/quickcart.php",

		   data: $(this).parent().parent().parent().serialize(),

		   dataType: "json",

		   success: function(res){

			   if(res.status)

			   {

				   $('#_ajax_div_items').html(res.totalnum);

				   $('._ajax_div_items').html(res.totalnum);

				   _this.tip(res.msg, 15, -1, 2000); 
                   timeId = setTimeout(function() {
						_this.parent().parent().parent().parent().parent().hide();
					}, 3000);	
				var quickaddtocart_obj = _this.parent().parent().parent().parent().parent().parent().find('.quickaddtocart');
				var input_num_obj = _this.parent().parent().find('input[name="num"]');
				ga('ec:addProduct', {      
				   'id': quickaddtocart_obj.attr('data_itemno'),					// SKU   
				   'name': quickaddtocart_obj.attr('data_name'),	// 
				   'category': quickaddtocart_obj.attr('ga_categorys'),				// 
				   'brand': 'DL',						// 
				   'price': quickaddtocart_obj.attr('data_price'),				//   
				   'quantity': input_num_obj.val() ? input_num_obj.val():1,				//   
				   'variant':res.variant
				   });   
				ga('ec:setAction', 'add');   
				ga('send', 'event', 'UX', 'click', 'add to cart');     // Send data using an event.
                
			   }

			   else

			   {

				   _this.tip(res.msg, 15, -1, 2000); 

			   }			   

		   }

		}); 

   });

   $('.favorite_btn').live('click',function(){

		var _this = $(this);

		$.ajax({

		   type: "POST",

		   url: "/quickcart.php",

		   data: {quickaddtofavorite:1,id:_this.attr('pid')},

		   dataType: "json",

		   success: function(res){

			   if(res.status)

			   {

				   _this.tip(res.msg, 15, 0, 2000); 

			   }

			   else

			   {

				   _this.tip(res.msg, 15, 0, 2000); 

			   }			   

		   }

		}); 

   });

   $('.quickcart input.cancel_btn').live('click',function(){$(this).parent().parent().parent().parent().parent().hide();});

});

function quickcartsizechange(obj,allstock)

{

	if($(obj).val())

	{

		size = $(obj).val() ;

		stock = $(obj).find('option:selected').attr('stock');

		$(obj).parent().parent().parent().find('.stock').html($(obj).val()+' : '+stock+' Pcs');

	}

	else

	{

		$(obj).parent().parent().parent().find('.stock').html('All '+allstock+' Pcs');

	}

}

</script>

        <script language=javascript>
function cshow(id)
{
var obj=document.getElementById(id);
if (obj.style.display=="none")
 {obj.style.display="";}
else
 {obj.style.display="none";}
}
function startlist(root)
{  
	//alert(root.getElementsByTagName("li"));
  var objSon = new Array();
  var objSon = root.getElementsByTagName("li") ;
  for(var i=0;i<=objSon.length-1;i++)
    {
          if(objSon[i].lastChild.nodeName.toLowerCase()=="ul")
	        { 
			  objSon[i].onmouseover=function(){  this.lastChild.style.display='block'; $(this).addClass("aulli1on");}
	          objSon[i].onmouseout=function(){  this.lastChild.style.display='none'; $(this).removeClass("aulli1on"); }
			  //startlist(objSon[i].lastChild);
			}
	}
}

 $(".aulli1").each(function(){
		$(this).hover(
			function(){
				$(this).find(".aliul1").show();
				$(this).addClass("aulli1on");
				},
			function(){
				$(this).find(".aliul1").hide();
				$(this).removeClass("aulli1on");
				}
	    );					
});
</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
$(function(){
	$(".like_sold .like").click(function(){
		var _this = this;
		$.ajax({
		   type: "GET",
		   url: "/index.php?action=add_favorite",
		   data: {pid:$(this).attr('data_id'),ajax:1},
		   dataType: "json",
		   success: function(res){
			 if(res.status)
			 {
				 var old_num = $(_this).text();
				 old_num = old_num.replace("Like(","");
				 old_num = old_num.replace(")","");
				 old_num = parseInt(old_num);
				 old_num = old_num+1;
				 $(_this).text("Like("+old_num+")");
				 $(_this).tip(res.msg, 15, 0, 2000);
			 }
			 else
			 {
				 $(_this).tip(res.msg, 15, 0, 2000);
			 }
		   }
		});
	});
});
function createAjaxLoading()
{
    $('<div/>').appendTo(document.body).addClass('ajax_loading');
}
function removeAjaxLoading()
{
    $('.ajax_loading').remove();
}
</script></div>

.zoom2 { border:1px #A6A6A6 solid}

</style><script type="text/javascript" src="/skin/default/pic/jq.puzz.js"></script>

<script type="text/javascript">

$(function(){

	$('.quickaddtocart').each(function(){

		$(this).click(function(){

			var _this = $(this);	

			var _parent = $(this).parent().parent();	

			var _quickbox = _parent.find('.quickcart_box');

			if(_quickbox.html()=='')

			{

				_quickbox.show();

				_quickbox.css('position','absolute');

				_quickbox.html('Loading...');

				var size = _this.attr('data');

				result =  eval("("+size+")");

				var carthtml = '<div class="quickcart">   <form>   <input name="id" type="hidden" value="'+_this.attr('pid')+'" />   <input name="quickaddtocart" type="hidden" value="1" />   <ul>';

				carthtml +='        <li>            <div class="property_name">Size : <input name="key0" type="hidden" value="Size" /></div>            <div class="property_value"><select id="style0" name="style0" onchange="quickcartsizechange(this,'+_this.attr('stock')+');"><option value="">Select Size</option>';

                                var total_count = 0;

				for(var key in result)

				{

					result[key] = parseInt(result[key]);	

				    if(result[key]>0)

					{

                                            total_count++;

						if(key=='os')

							size = "one size";

						else

							size = key ;

						carthtml += '<option value="'+size+'" stock="'+result[key]+'">'+size+'</option>';

					}

				}

				carthtml += '</select></div>        </li>';

				carthtml +='        <li>            <div class="property_name">Qty :</div>            <div class="property_value"><input name="num" value="1" /></div>        </li>';

				carthtml +='        <li>            <div class="property_name">Stock :</div>            <div class="property_value"><span class="stock">All '+_this.attr('stock')+' Pcs</span></div>        </li>';

				carthtml +='<li>            <input type="button" value="Submit" class="submit_btn" />            <input type="button" value="Cancel" class="cancel_btn" />        </li>   </ul>   </form></div>';

				_quickbox.html(carthtml);

				_quickbox.css('position','relative');

                                if(total_count==1)

                                {

                                    _quickbox.find('#style0').val(_quickbox.find('#style0').find('option').eq(1).attr('value'));

                                    _quickbox.find('#style0').change();

                                }

			}

			else

			{

				_quickbox.show();

		    }

		});

	});

   $('.quickcart input.submit_btn').live('click',function(){

		var is_submit = true;

		var _this = $(this);

		$(this).parent().parent().parent().find('select').each(function(){

			if(!$(this).val())

			{

				$(this).tip("Please Select " +  $(this).parent().siblings('.property_name').find('input').val(), 15, 0, 2000); 

				is_submit = false;

				return;

			}

		});	

		if(!is_submit)

		{

			return;

		}

		$.ajax({

		   type: "POST",

		   url: "/quickcart.php",

		   data: $(this).parent().parent().parent().serialize(),

		   dataType: "json",

		   success: function(res){

			   if(res.status)

			   {

				   $('#_ajax_div_items').html(res.totalnum);

				   $('._ajax_div_items').html(res.totalnum);

				   _this.tip(res.msg, 15, -1, 2000); 
                   timeId = setTimeout(function() {
						_this.parent().parent().parent().parent().parent().hide();
					}, 3000);	
				var quickaddtocart_obj = _this.parent().parent().parent().parent().parent().parent().find('.quickaddtocart');
				var input_num_obj = _this.parent().parent().find('input[name="num"]');
				ga('ec:addProduct', {      
				   'id': quickaddtocart_obj.attr('data_itemno'),					// SKU   
				   'name': quickaddtocart_obj.attr('data_name'),	// 
				   'category': quickaddtocart_obj.attr('ga_categorys'),				// 
				   'brand': 'DL',						// 
				   'price': quickaddtocart_obj.attr('data_price'),				//   
				   'quantity': input_num_obj.val() ? input_num_obj.val():1,				//   
				   'variant':res.variant
				   });   
				ga('ec:setAction', 'add');   
				ga('send', 'event', 'UX', 'click', 'add to cart');     // Send data using an event.
                
			   }

			   else

			   {

				   _this.tip(res.msg, 15, -1, 2000); 

			   }			   

		   }

		}); 

   });

   $('.favorite_btn').live('click',function(){

		var _this = $(this);

		$.ajax({

		   type: "POST",

		   url: "/quickcart.php",

		   data: {quickaddtofavorite:1,id:_this.attr('pid')},

		   dataType: "json",

		   success: function(res){

			   if(res.status)

			   {

				   _this.tip(res.msg, 15, 0, 2000); 

			   }

			   else

			   {

				   _this.tip(res.msg, 15, 0, 2000); 

			   }			   

		   }

		}); 

   });

   $('.quickcart input.cancel_btn').live('click',function(){$(this).parent().parent().parent().parent().parent().hide();});

});

function quickcartsizechange(obj,allstock)

{

	if($(obj).val())

	{

		size = $(obj).val() ;

		stock = $(obj).find('option:selected').attr('stock');

		$(obj).parent().parent().parent().find('.stock').html($(obj).val()+' : '+stock+' Pcs');

	}

	else

	{

		$(obj).parent().parent().parent().find('.stock').html('All '+allstock+' Pcs');

	}

}

</script>

                                onSelect: function(suggestion) {
                                var keywords = $('#search_keywords').val();
                                keywords = escape(escape(suggestion.value));
                                window.location.href = '/Search-'+keywords+'/';
                                },
                                onFocus: function(){
                                    return false;
                                }
                        });
                        $('#autocomplete-submit').submit(function() {
                            var keywords = $('#search_keywords').val();
                            keywords = escape(escape(keywords));
                            location.href = '/Search-'+keywords+'/';
                            return false;
                            //$('#autocomplete-submit').attr('action', '/Search/' + keywords + '/list-r1.html');
                        });
                        $('#btn-autocomplete').click(function() {
                            var keywords = $('#search_keywords').val();
                            keywords = escape(escape(keywords));
                            location.href = '/Search-'+keywords+'/';
                            //$('#autocomplete-submit').attr('action', '/Search/' + keywords + '/list-r1.html');
                        });
                    </script>

        <script language=javascript>
function cshow(id)
{
var obj=document.getElementById(id);
if (obj.style.display=="none")
 {obj.style.display="";}
else
 {obj.style.display="none";}
}
function startlist(root)
{  
	//alert(root.getElementsByTagName("li"));
  var objSon = new Array();
  var objSon = root.getElementsByTagName("li") ;
  for(var i=0;i<=objSon.length-1;i++)
    {
          if(objSon[i].lastChild.nodeName.toLowerCase()=="ul")
	        { 
			  objSon[i].onmouseover=function(){  this.lastChild.style.display='block'; $(this).addClass("aulli1on");}
	          objSon[i].onmouseout=function(){  this.lastChild.style.display='none'; $(this).removeClass("aulli1on"); }
			  //startlist(objSon[i].lastChild);
			}
	}
}

 $(".aulli1").each(function(){
		$(this).hover(
			function(){
				$(this).find(".aliul1").show();
				$(this).addClass("aulli1on");
				},
			function(){
				$(this).find(".aliul1").hide();
				$(this).removeClass("aulli1on");
				}
	    );					
});
</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
$(function(){
	$(".like_sold .like").click(function(){
		var _this = this;
		$.ajax({
		   type: "GET",
		   url: "/index.php?action=add_favorite",
		   data: {pid:$(this).attr('data_id'),ajax:1},
		   dataType: "json",
		   success: function(res){
			 if(res.status)
			 {
				 var old_num = $(_this).text();
				 old_num = old_num.replace("Like(","");
				 old_num = old_num.replace(")","");
				 old_num = parseInt(old_num);
				 old_num = old_num+1;
				 $(_this).text("Like("+old_num+")");
				 $(_this).tip(res.msg, 15, 0, 2000);
			 }
			 else
			 {
				 $(_this).tip(res.msg, 15, 0, 2000);
			 }
		   }
		});
	});
});
function createAjaxLoading()
{
    $('<div/>').appendTo(document.body).addClass('ajax_loading');
}
function removeAjaxLoading()
{
    $('.ajax_loading').remove();
}
</script></div>

.zoom2 { border:1px #A6A6A6 solid}

</style><script type="text/javascript" src="/skin/default/pic/jq.puzz.js"></script>

<script type="text/javascript">

$(function(){

	$('.quickaddtocart').each(function(){

		$(this).click(function(){

			var _this = $(this);	

			var _parent = $(this).parent().parent();	

			var _quickbox = _parent.find('.quickcart_box');

			if(_quickbox.html()=='')

			{

				_quickbox.show();

				_quickbox.css('position','absolute');

				_quickbox.html('Loading...');

				var size = _this.attr('data');

				result =  eval("("+size+")");

				var carthtml = '<div class="quickcart">   <form>   <input name="id" type="hidden" value="'+_this.attr('pid')+'" />   <input name="quickaddtocart" type="hidden" value="1" />   <ul>';

				carthtml +='        <li>            <div class="property_name">Size : <input name="key0" type="hidden" value="Size" /></div>            <div class="property_value"><select id="style0" name="style0" onchange="quickcartsizechange(this,'+_this.attr('stock')+');"><option value="">Select Size</option>';

                                var total_count = 0;

				for(var key in result)

				{

					result[key] = parseInt(result[key]);	

				    if(result[key]>0)

					{

                                            total_count++;

						if(key=='os')

							size = "one size";

						else

							size = key ;

						carthtml += '<option value="'+size+'" stock="'+result[key]+'">'+size+'</option>';

					}

				}

				carthtml += '</select></div>        </li>';

				carthtml +='        <li>            <div class="property_name">Qty :</div>            <div class="property_value"><input name="num" value="1" /></div>        </li>';

				carthtml +='        <li>            <div class="property_name">Stock :</div>            <div class="property_value"><span class="stock">All '+_this.attr('stock')+' Pcs</span></div>        </li>';

				carthtml +='<li>            <input type="button" value="Submit" class="submit_btn" />            <input type="button" value="Cancel" class="cancel_btn" />        </li>   </ul>   </form></div>';

				_quickbox.html(carthtml);

				_quickbox.css('position','relative');

                                if(total_count==1)

                                {

                                    _quickbox.find('#style0').val(_quickbox.find('#style0').find('option').eq(1).attr('value'));

                                    _quickbox.find('#style0').change();

                                }

			}

			else

			{

				_quickbox.show();

		    }

		});

	});

   $('.quickcart input.submit_btn').live('click',function(){

		var is_submit = true;

		var _this = $(this);

		$(this).parent().parent().parent().find('select').each(function(){

			if(!$(this).val())

			{

				$(this).tip("Please Select " +  $(this).parent().siblings('.property_name').find('input').val(), 15, 0, 2000); 

				is_submit = false;

				return;

			}

		});	

		if(!is_submit)

		{

			return;

		}

		$.ajax({

		   type: "POST",

		   url: "/quickcart.php",

		   data: $(this).parent().parent().parent().serialize(),

		   dataType: "json",

		   success: function(res){

			   if(res.status)

			   {

				   $('#_ajax_div_items').html(res.totalnum);

				   $('._ajax_div_items').html(res.totalnum);

				   _this.tip(res.msg, 15, -1, 2000); 
                   timeId = setTimeout(function() {
						_this.parent().parent().parent().parent().parent().hide();
					}, 3000);	
				var quickaddtocart_obj = _this.parent().parent().parent().parent().parent().parent().find('.quickaddtocart');
				var input_num_obj = _this.parent().parent().find('input[name="num"]');
				ga('ec:addProduct', {      
				   'id': quickaddtocart_obj.attr('data_itemno'),					// SKU   
				   'name': quickaddtocart_obj.attr('data_name'),	// 
				   'category': quickaddtocart_obj.attr('ga_categorys'),				// 
				   'brand': 'DL',						// 
				   'price': quickaddtocart_obj.attr('data_price'),				//   
				   'quantity': input_num_obj.val() ? input_num_obj.val():1,				//   
				   'variant':res.variant
				   });   
				ga('ec:setAction', 'add');   
				ga('send', 'event', 'UX', 'click', 'add to cart');     // Send data using an event.
                
			   }

			   else

			   {

				   _this.tip(res.msg, 15, -1, 2000); 

			   }			   

		   }

		}); 

   });

   $('.favorite_btn').live('click',function(){

		var _this = $(this);

		$.ajax({

		   type: "POST",

		   url: "/quickcart.php",

		   data: {quickaddtofavorite:1,id:_this.attr('pid')},

		   dataType: "json",

		   success: function(res){

			   if(res.status)

			   {

				   _this.tip(res.msg, 15, 0, 2000); 

			   }

			   else

			   {

				   _this.tip(res.msg, 15, 0, 2000); 

			   }			   

		   }

		}); 

   });

   $('.quickcart input.cancel_btn').live('click',function(){$(this).parent().parent().parent().parent().parent().hide();});

});

function quickcartsizechange(obj,allstock)

{

	if($(obj).val())

	{

		size = $(obj).val() ;

		stock = $(obj).find('option:selected').attr('stock');

		$(obj).parent().parent().parent().find('.stock').html($(obj).val()+' : '+stock+' Pcs');

	}

	else

	{

		$(obj).parent().parent().parent().find('.stock').html('All '+allstock+' Pcs');

	}

}

</script>

    $('ul.products li').not('.other').hover(

		function(){

        $(window).scroll(function() {
            if ($(this).scrollTop() >= 30) {
                $('#top_float').show();
            } else {
                $('#top_float').hide();
            }
        });

        <script language=javascript>
function cshow(id)
{
var obj=document.getElementById(id);
if (obj.style.display=="none")
 {obj.style.display="";}
else
 {obj.style.display="none";}
}
function startlist(root)
{  
	//alert(root.getElementsByTagName("li"));
  var objSon = new Array();
  var objSon = root.getElementsByTagName("li") ;
  for(var i=0;i<=objSon.length-1;i++)
    {
          if(objSon[i].lastChild.nodeName.toLowerCase()=="ul")
	        { 
			  objSon[i].onmouseover=function(){  this.lastChild.style.display='block'; $(this).addClass("aulli1on");}
	          objSon[i].onmouseout=function(){  this.lastChild.style.display='none'; $(this).removeClass("aulli1on"); }
			  //startlist(objSon[i].lastChild);
			}
	}
}

 $(".aulli1").each(function(){
		$(this).hover(
			function(){
				$(this).find(".aliul1").show();
				$(this).addClass("aulli1on");
				},
			function(){
				$(this).find(".aliul1").hide();
				$(this).removeClass("aulli1on");
				}
	    );					
});
</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
$(function(){
	$(".like_sold .like").click(function(){
		var _this = this;
		$.ajax({
		   type: "GET",
		   url: "/index.php?action=add_favorite",
		   data: {pid:$(this).attr('data_id'),ajax:1},
		   dataType: "json",
		   success: function(res){
			 if(res.status)
			 {
				 var old_num = $(_this).text();
				 old_num = old_num.replace("Like(","");
				 old_num = old_num.replace(")","");
				 old_num = parseInt(old_num);
				 old_num = old_num+1;
				 $(_this).text("Like("+old_num+")");
				 $(_this).tip(res.msg, 15, 0, 2000);
			 }
			 else
			 {
				 $(_this).tip(res.msg, 15, 0, 2000);
			 }
		   }
		});
	});
});
function createAjaxLoading()
{
    $('<div/>').appendTo(document.body).addClass('ajax_loading');
}
function removeAjaxLoading()
{
    $('.ajax_loading').remove();
}
</script></div>

<script type="text/javascript">

$(function(){

	$('.quickaddtocart').each(function(){

		$(this).click(function(){

			var _this = $(this);	

			var _parent = $(this).parent().parent();	

			var _quickbox = _parent.find('.quickcart_box');

			if(_quickbox.html()=='')

			{

				_quickbox.show();

				_quickbox.css('position','absolute');

				_quickbox.html('Loading...');

				var size = _this.attr('data');

				result =  eval("("+size+")");

				var carthtml = '<div class="quickcart">   <form>   <input name="id" type="hidden" value="'+_this.attr('pid')+'" />   <input name="quickaddtocart" type="hidden" value="1" />   <ul>';

				carthtml +='        <li>            <div class="property_name">Size : <input name="key0" type="hidden" value="Size" /></div>            <div class="property_value"><select id="style0" name="style0" onchange="quickcartsizechange(this,'+_this.attr('stock')+');"><option value="">Select Size</option>';

                                var total_count = 0;

				for(var key in result)

				{

					result[key] = parseInt(result[key]);	

				    if(result[key]>0)

					{

                                            total_count++;

						if(key=='os')

							size = "one size";

						else

							size = key ;

						carthtml += '<option value="'+size+'" stock="'+result[key]+'">'+size+'</option>';

					}

				}

				carthtml += '</select></div>        </li>';

				carthtml +='        <li>            <div class="property_name">Qty :</div>            <div class="property_value"><input name="num" value="1" /></div>        </li>';

				carthtml +='        <li>            <div class="property_name">Stock :</div>            <div class="property_value"><span class="stock">All '+_this.attr('stock')+' Pcs</span></div>        </li>';

				carthtml +='<li>            <input type="button" value="Submit" class="submit_btn" />            <input type="button" value="Cancel" class="cancel_btn" />        </li>   </ul>   </form></div>';

				_quickbox.html(carthtml);

				_quickbox.css('position','relative');

                                if(total_count==1)

                                {

                                    _quickbox.find('#style0').val(_quickbox.find('#style0').find('option').eq(1).attr('value'));

                                    _quickbox.find('#style0').change();

                                }

			}

			else

			{

				_quickbox.show();

		    }

		});

	});

   $('.quickcart input.submit_btn').live('click',function(){

		var is_submit = true;

		var _this = $(this);

		$(this).parent().parent().parent().find('select').each(function(){

			if(!$(this).val())

			{

				$(this).tip("Please Select " +  $(this).parent().siblings('.property_name').find('input').val(), 15, 0, 2000); 

				is_submit = false;

				return;

			}

		});	

		if(!is_submit)

		{

			return;

		}

		$.ajax({

		   type: "POST",

		   url: "/quickcart.php",

		   data: $(this).parent().parent().parent().serialize(),

		   dataType: "json",

		   success: function(res){

			   if(res.status)

			   {

				   $('#_ajax_div_items').html(res.totalnum);

				   $('._ajax_div_items').html(res.totalnum);

				   _this.tip(res.msg, 15, -1, 2000); 
                   timeId = setTimeout(function() {
						_this.parent().parent().parent().parent().parent().hide();
					}, 3000);	
				var quickaddtocart_obj = _this.parent().parent().parent().parent().parent().parent().find('.quickaddtocart');
				var input_num_obj = _this.parent().parent().find('input[name="num"]');
				ga('ec:addProduct', {      
				   'id': quickaddtocart_obj.attr('data_itemno'),					// SKU   
				   'name': quickaddtocart_obj.attr('data_name'),	// 
				   'category': quickaddtocart_obj.attr('ga_categorys'),				// 
				   'brand': 'DL',						// 
				   'price': quickaddtocart_obj.attr('data_price'),				//   
				   'quantity': input_num_obj.val() ? input_num_obj.val():1,				//   
				   'variant':res.variant
				   });   
				ga('ec:setAction', 'add');   
				ga('send', 'event', 'UX', 'click', 'add to cart');     // Send data using an event.
                
			   }

			   else

			   {

				   _this.tip(res.msg, 15, -1, 2000); 

			   }			   

		   }

		}); 

   });

   $('.favorite_btn').live('click',function(){

		var _this = $(this);

		$.ajax({

		   type: "POST",

		   url: "/quickcart.php",

		   data: {quickaddtofavorite:1,id:_this.attr('pid')},

		   dataType: "json",

		   success: function(res){

			   if(res.status)

			   {

				   _this.tip(res.msg, 15, 0, 2000); 

			   }

			   else

			   {

				   _this.tip(res.msg, 15, 0, 2000); 

			   }			   

		   }

		}); 

   });

   $('.quickcart input.cancel_btn').live('click',function(){$(this).parent().parent().parent().parent().parent().hide();});

});

function quickcartsizechange(obj,allstock)

{

	if($(obj).val())

	{

		size = $(obj).val() ;

		stock = $(obj).find('option:selected').attr('stock');

		$(obj).parent().parent().parent().find('.stock').html($(obj).val()+' : '+stock+' Pcs');

	}

	else

	{

		$(obj).parent().parent().parent().find('.stock').html('All '+allstock+' Pcs');

	}

}

</script>

    $('ul.products li').not('.other').hover(

		function(){

        <script language=javascript>
function cshow(id)
{
var obj=document.getElementById(id);
if (obj.style.display=="none")
 {obj.style.display="";}
else
 {obj.style.display="none";}
}
function startlist(root)
{  
	//alert(root.getElementsByTagName("li"));
  var objSon = new Array();
  var objSon = root.getElementsByTagName("li") ;
  for(var i=0;i<=objSon.length-1;i++)
    {
          if(objSon[i].lastChild.nodeName.toLowerCase()=="ul")
	        { 
			  objSon[i].onmouseover=function(){  this.lastChild.style.display='block'; $(this).addClass("aulli1on");}
	          objSon[i].onmouseout=function(){  this.lastChild.style.display='none'; $(this).removeClass("aulli1on"); }
			  //startlist(objSon[i].lastChild);
			}
	}
}

 $(".aulli1").each(function(){
		$(this).hover(
			function(){
				$(this).find(".aliul1").show();
				$(this).addClass("aulli1on");
				},
			function(){
				$(this).find(".aliul1").hide();
				$(this).removeClass("aulli1on");
				}
	    );					
});
</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
$(function(){
	$(".like_sold .like").click(function(){
		var _this = this;
		$.ajax({
		   type: "GET",
		   url: "/index.php?action=add_favorite",
		   data: {pid:$(this).attr('data_id'),ajax:1},
		   dataType: "json",
		   success: function(res){
			 if(res.status)
			 {
				 var old_num = $(_this).text();
				 old_num = old_num.replace("Like(","");
				 old_num = old_num.replace(")","");
				 old_num = parseInt(old_num);
				 old_num = old_num+1;
				 $(_this).text("Like("+old_num+")");
				 $(_this).tip(res.msg, 15, 0, 2000);
			 }
			 else
			 {
				 $(_this).tip(res.msg, 15, 0, 2000);
			 }
		   }
		});
	});
});
function createAjaxLoading()
{
    $('<div/>').appendTo(document.body).addClass('ajax_loading');
}
function removeAjaxLoading()
{
    $('.ajax_loading').remove();
}
</script></div>

</style><script type="text/javascript" src="/skin/default/pic/jq.puzz.js"></script>

<script type="text/javascript">

$(function(){

	$('.quickaddtocart').each(function(){

		$(this).click(function(){

			var _this = $(this);	

			var _parent = $(this).parent().parent();	

			var _quickbox = _parent.find('.quickcart_box');

			if(_quickbox.html()=='')

			{

				_quickbox.show();

				_quickbox.css('position','absolute');

				_quickbox.html('Loading...');

				var size = _this.attr('data');

				result =  eval("("+size+")");

				var carthtml = '<div class="quickcart">   <form>   <input name="id" type="hidden" value="'+_this.attr('pid')+'" />   <input name="quickaddtocart" type="hidden" value="1" />   <ul>';

				carthtml +='        <li>            <div class="property_name">Size : <input name="key0" type="hidden" value="Size" /></div>            <div class="property_value"><select id="style0" name="style0" onchange="quickcartsizechange(this,'+_this.attr('stock')+');"><option value="">Select Size</option>';

                                var total_count = 0;

				for(var key in result)

				{

					result[key] = parseInt(result[key]);	

				    if(result[key]>0)

					{

                                            total_count++;

						if(key=='os')

							size = "one size";

						else

							size = key ;

						carthtml += '<option value="'+size+'" stock="'+result[key]+'">'+size+'</option>';

					}

				}

				carthtml += '</select></div>        </li>';

				carthtml +='        <li>            <div class="property_name">Qty :</div>            <div class="property_value"><input name="num" value="1" /></div>        </li>';

				carthtml +='        <li>            <div class="property_name">Stock :</div>            <div class="property_value"><span class="stock">All '+_this.attr('stock')+' Pcs</span></div>        </li>';

				carthtml +='<li>            <input type="button" value="Submit" class="submit_btn" />            <input type="button" value="Cancel" class="cancel_btn" />        </li>   </ul>   </form></div>';

				_quickbox.html(carthtml);

				_quickbox.css('position','relative');

                                if(total_count==1)

                                {

                                    _quickbox.find('#style0').val(_quickbox.find('#style0').find('option').eq(1).attr('value'));

                                    _quickbox.find('#style0').change();

                                }

			}

			else

			{

				_quickbox.show();

		    }

		});

	});

   $('.quickcart input.submit_btn').live('click',function(){

		var is_submit = true;

		var _this = $(this);

		$(this).parent().parent().parent().find('select').each(function(){

			if(!$(this).val())

			{

				$(this).tip("Please Select " +  $(this).parent().siblings('.property_name').find('input').val(), 15, 0, 2000); 

				is_submit = false;

				return;

			}

		});	

		if(!is_submit)

		{

			return;

		}

		$.ajax({

		   type: "POST",

		   url: "/quickcart.php",

		   data: $(this).parent().parent().parent().serialize(),

		   dataType: "json",

		   success: function(res){

			   if(res.status)

			   {

				   $('#_ajax_div_items').html(res.totalnum);

				   $('._ajax_div_items').html(res.totalnum);

				   _this.tip(res.msg, 15, -1, 2000); 
                   timeId = setTimeout(function() {
						_this.parent().parent().parent().parent().parent().hide();
					}, 3000);	
				var quickaddtocart_obj = _this.parent().parent().parent().parent().parent().parent().find('.quickaddtocart');
				var input_num_obj = _this.parent().parent().find('input[name="num"]');
				ga('ec:addProduct', {      
				   'id': quickaddtocart_obj.attr('data_itemno'),					// SKU   
				   'name': quickaddtocart_obj.attr('data_name'),	// 
				   'category': quickaddtocart_obj.attr('ga_categorys'),				// 
				   'brand': 'DL',						// 
				   'price': quickaddtocart_obj.attr('data_price'),				//   
				   'quantity': input_num_obj.val() ? input_num_obj.val():1,				//   
				   'variant':res.variant
				   });   
				ga('ec:setAction', 'add');   
				ga('send', 'event', 'UX', 'click', 'add to cart');     // Send data using an event.
                
			   }

			   else

			   {

				   _this.tip(res.msg, 15, -1, 2000); 

			   }			   

		   }

		}); 

   });

   $('.favorite_btn').live('click',function(){

		var _this = $(this);

		$.ajax({

		   type: "POST",

		   url: "/quickcart.php",

		   data: {quickaddtofavorite:1,id:_this.attr('pid')},

		   dataType: "json",

		   success: function(res){

			   if(res.status)

			   {

				   _this.tip(res.msg, 15, 0, 2000); 

			   }

			   else

			   {

				   _this.tip(res.msg, 15, 0, 2000); 

			   }			   

		   }

		}); 

   });

   $('.quickcart input.cancel_btn').live('click',function(){$(this).parent().parent().parent().parent().parent().hide();});

});

function quickcartsizechange(obj,allstock)

{

	if($(obj).val())

	{

		size = $(obj).val() ;

		stock = $(obj).find('option:selected').attr('stock');

		$(obj).parent().parent().parent().find('.stock').html($(obj).val()+' : '+stock+' Pcs');

	}

	else

	{

		$(obj).parent().parent().parent().find('.stock').html('All '+allstock+' Pcs');

	}

}

</script>

    $('ul.products li').not('.other').hover(

		function(){

        <script language=javascript>
function cshow(id)
{
var obj=document.getElementById(id);
if (obj.style.display=="none")
 {obj.style.display="";}
else
 {obj.style.display="none";}
}
function startlist(root)
{  
	//alert(root.getElementsByTagName("li"));
  var objSon = new Array();
  var objSon = root.getElementsByTagName("li") ;
  for(var i=0;i<=objSon.length-1;i++)
    {
          if(objSon[i].lastChild.nodeName.toLowerCase()=="ul")
	        { 
			  objSon[i].onmouseover=function(){  this.lastChild.style.display='block'; $(this).addClass("aulli1on");}
	          objSon[i].onmouseout=function(){  this.lastChild.style.display='none'; $(this).removeClass("aulli1on"); }
			  //startlist(objSon[i].lastChild);
			}
	}
}

 $(".aulli1").each(function(){
		$(this).hover(
			function(){
				$(this).find(".aliul1").show();
				$(this).addClass("aulli1on");
				},
			function(){
				$(this).find(".aliul1").hide();
				$(this).removeClass("aulli1on");
				}
	    );					
});
</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
$(function(){
	$(".like_sold .like").click(function(){
		var _this = this;
		$.ajax({
		   type: "GET",
		   url: "/index.php?action=add_favorite",
		   data: {pid:$(this).attr('data_id'),ajax:1},
		   dataType: "json",
		   success: function(res){
			 if(res.status)
			 {
				 var old_num = $(_this).text();
				 old_num = old_num.replace("Like(","");
				 old_num = old_num.replace(")","");
				 old_num = parseInt(old_num);
				 old_num = old_num+1;
				 $(_this).text("Like("+old_num+")");
				 $(_this).tip(res.msg, 15, 0, 2000);
			 }
			 else
			 {
				 $(_this).tip(res.msg, 15, 0, 2000);
			 }
		   }
		});
	});
});
function createAjaxLoading()
{
    $('<div/>').appendTo(document.body).addClass('ajax_loading');
}
function removeAjaxLoading()
{
    $('.ajax_loading').remove();
}
</script></div>

</style><script type="text/javascript" src="/skin/default/pic/jq.puzz.js"></script>

<script type="text/javascript">

$(function(){

	$('.quickaddtocart').each(function(){

		$(this).click(function(){

			var _this = $(this);	

			var _parent = $(this).parent().parent();	

			var _quickbox = _parent.find('.quickcart_box');

			if(_quickbox.html()=='')

			{

				_quickbox.show();

				_quickbox.css('position','absolute');

				_quickbox.html('Loading...');

				var size = _this.attr('data');

				result =  eval("("+size+")");

				var carthtml = '<div class="quickcart">   <form>   <input name="id" type="hidden" value="'+_this.attr('pid')+'" />   <input name="quickaddtocart" type="hidden" value="1" />   <ul>';

				carthtml +='        <li>            <div class="property_name">Size : <input name="key0" type="hidden" value="Size" /></div>            <div class="property_value"><select id="style0" name="style0" onchange="quickcartsizechange(this,'+_this.attr('stock')+');"><option value="">Select Size</option>';

                                var total_count = 0;

				for(var key in result)

				{

					result[key] = parseInt(result[key]);	

				    if(result[key]>0)

					{

                                            total_count++;

						if(key=='os')

							size = "one size";

						else

							size = key ;

						carthtml += '<option value="'+size+'" stock="'+result[key]+'">'+size+'</option>';

					}

				}

				carthtml += '</select></div>        </li>';

				carthtml +='        <li>            <div class="property_name">Qty :</div>            <div class="property_value"><input name="num" value="1" /></div>        </li>';

				carthtml +='        <li>            <div class="property_name">Stock :</div>            <div class="property_value"><span class="stock">All '+_this.attr('stock')+' Pcs</span></div>        </li>';

				carthtml +='<li>            <input type="button" value="Submit" class="submit_btn" />            <input type="button" value="Cancel" class="cancel_btn" />        </li>   </ul>   </form></div>';

				_quickbox.html(carthtml);

				_quickbox.css('position','relative');

                                if(total_count==1)

                                {

                                    _quickbox.find('#style0').val(_quickbox.find('#style0').find('option').eq(1).attr('value'));

                                    _quickbox.find('#style0').change();

                                }

			}

			else

			{

				_quickbox.show();

		    }

		});

	});

   $('.quickcart input.submit_btn').live('click',function(){

		var is_submit = true;

		var _this = $(this);

		$(this).parent().parent().parent().find('select').each(function(){

			if(!$(this).val())

			{

				$(this).tip("Please Select " +  $(this).parent().siblings('.property_name').find('input').val(), 15, 0, 2000); 

				is_submit = false;

				return;

			}

		});	

		if(!is_submit)

		{

			return;

		}

		$.ajax({

		   type: "POST",

		   url: "/quickcart.php",

		   data: $(this).parent().parent().parent().serialize(),

		   dataType: "json",

		   success: function(res){

			   if(res.status)

			   {

				   $('#_ajax_div_items').html(res.totalnum);

				   $('._ajax_div_items').html(res.totalnum);

				   _this.tip(res.msg, 15, -1, 2000); 
                   timeId = setTimeout(function() {
						_this.parent().parent().parent().parent().parent().hide();
					}, 3000);	
				var quickaddtocart_obj = _this.parent().parent().parent().parent().parent().parent().find('.quickaddtocart');
				var input_num_obj = _this.parent().parent().find('input[name="num"]');
				ga('ec:addProduct', {      
				   'id': quickaddtocart_obj.attr('data_itemno'),					// SKU   
				   'name': quickaddtocart_obj.attr('data_name'),	// 
				   'category': quickaddtocart_obj.attr('ga_categorys'),				// 
				   'brand': 'DL',						// 
				   'price': quickaddtocart_obj.attr('data_price'),				//   
				   'quantity': input_num_obj.val() ? input_num_obj.val():1,				//   
				   'variant':res.variant
				   });   
				ga('ec:setAction', 'add');   
				ga('send', 'event', 'UX', 'click', 'add to cart');     // Send data using an event.
                
			   }

			   else

			   {

				   _this.tip(res.msg, 15, -1, 2000); 

			   }			   

		   }

		}); 

   });

   $('.favorite_btn').live('click',function(){

		var _this = $(this);

		$.ajax({

		   type: "POST",

		   url: "/quickcart.php",

		   data: {quickaddtofavorite:1,id:_this.attr('pid')},

		   dataType: "json",

		   success: function(res){

			   if(res.status)

			   {

				   _this.tip(res.msg, 15, 0, 2000); 

			   }

			   else

			   {

				   _this.tip(res.msg, 15, 0, 2000); 

			   }			   

		   }

		}); 

   });

   $('.quickcart input.cancel_btn').live('click',function(){$(this).parent().parent().parent().parent().parent().hide();});

});

function quickcartsizechange(obj,allstock)

{

	if($(obj).val())

	{

		size = $(obj).val() ;

		stock = $(obj).find('option:selected').attr('stock');

		$(obj).parent().parent().parent().find('.stock').html($(obj).val()+' : '+stock+' Pcs');

	}

	else

	{

		$(obj).parent().parent().parent().find('.stock').html('All '+allstock+' Pcs');

	}

}

</script>

        <script language=javascript>
function cshow(id)
{
var obj=document.getElementById(id);
if (obj.style.display=="none")
 {obj.style.display="";}
else
 {obj.style.display="none";}
}
function startlist(root)
{  
	//alert(root.getElementsByTagName("li"));
  var objSon = new Array();
  var objSon = root.getElementsByTagName("li") ;
  for(var i=0;i<=objSon.length-1;i++)
    {
          if(objSon[i].lastChild.nodeName.toLowerCase()=="ul")
	        { 
			  objSon[i].onmouseover=function(){  this.lastChild.style.display='block'; $(this).addClass("aulli1on");}
	          objSon[i].onmouseout=function(){  this.lastChild.style.display='none'; $(this).removeClass("aulli1on"); }
			  //startlist(objSon[i].lastChild);
			}
	}
}

 $(".aulli1").each(function(){
		$(this).hover(
			function(){
				$(this).find(".aliul1").show();
				$(this).addClass("aulli1on");
				},
			function(){
				$(this).find(".aliul1").hide();
				$(this).removeClass("aulli1on");
				}
	    );					
});
</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
$(function(){
	$(".like_sold .like").click(function(){
		var _this = this;
		$.ajax({
		   type: "GET",
		   url: "/index.php?action=add_favorite",
		   data: {pid:$(this).attr('data_id'),ajax:1},
		   dataType: "json",
		   success: function(res){
			 if(res.status)
			 {
				 var old_num = $(_this).text();
				 old_num = old_num.replace("Like(","");
				 old_num = old_num.replace(")","");
				 old_num = parseInt(old_num);
				 old_num = old_num+1;
				 $(_this).text("Like("+old_num+")");
				 $(_this).tip(res.msg, 15, 0, 2000);
			 }
			 else
			 {
				 $(_this).tip(res.msg, 15, 0, 2000);
			 }
		   }
		});
	});
});
function createAjaxLoading()
{
    $('<div/>').appendTo(document.body).addClass('ajax_loading');
}
function removeAjaxLoading()
{
    $('.ajax_loading').remove();
}
</script></div>

<script type="text/javascript">

$(function(){

	$('.quickaddtocart').each(function(){

		$(this).click(function(){

			var _this = $(this);	

			var _parent = $(this).parent().parent();	

			var _quickbox = _parent.find('.quickcart_box');

			if(_quickbox.html()=='')

			{

				_quickbox.show();

				_quickbox.css('position','absolute');

				_quickbox.html('Loading...');

				var size = _this.attr('data');

				result =  eval("("+size+")");

				var carthtml = '<div class="quickcart">   <form>   <input name="id" type="hidden" value="'+_this.attr('pid')+'" />   <input name="quickaddtocart" type="hidden" value="1" />   <ul>';

				carthtml +='        <li>            <div class="property_name">Size : <input name="key0" type="hidden" value="Size" /></div>            <div class="property_value"><select id="style0" name="style0" onchange="quickcartsizechange(this,'+_this.attr('stock')+');"><option value="">Select Size</option>';

                                var total_count = 0;

				for(var key in result)

				{

					result[key] = parseInt(result[key]);	

				    if(result[key]>0)

					{

                                            total_count++;

						if(key=='os')

							size = "one size";

						else

							size = key ;

						carthtml += '<option value="'+size+'" stock="'+result[key]+'">'+size+'</option>';

					}

				}

				carthtml += '</select></div>        </li>';

				carthtml +='        <li>            <div class="property_name">Qty :</div>            <div class="property_value"><input name="num" value="1" /></div>        </li>';

				carthtml +='        <li>            <div class="property_name">Stock :</div>            <div class="property_value"><span class="stock">All '+_this.attr('stock')+' Pcs</span></div>        </li>';

				carthtml +='<li>            <input type="button" value="Submit" class="submit_btn" />            <input type="button" value="Cancel" class="cancel_btn" />        </li>   </ul>   </form></div>';

				_quickbox.html(carthtml);

				_quickbox.css('position','relative');

                                if(total_count==1)

                                {

                                    _quickbox.find('#style0').val(_quickbox.find('#style0').find('option').eq(1).attr('value'));

                                    _quickbox.find('#style0').change();

                                }

			}

			else

			{

				_quickbox.show();

		    }

		});

	});

   $('.quickcart input.submit_btn').live('click',function(){

		var is_submit = true;

		var _this = $(this);

		$(this).parent().parent().parent().find('select').each(function(){

			if(!$(this).val())

			{

				$(this).tip("Please Select " +  $(this).parent().siblings('.property_name').find('input').val(), 15, 0, 2000); 

				is_submit = false;

				return;

			}

		});	

		if(!is_submit)

		{

			return;

		}

		$.ajax({

		   type: "POST",

		   url: "/quickcart.php",

		   data: $(this).parent().parent().parent().serialize(),

		   dataType: "json",

		   success: function(res){

			   if(res.status)

			   {

				   $('#_ajax_div_items').html(res.totalnum);

				   $('._ajax_div_items').html(res.totalnum);

				   _this.tip(res.msg, 15, -1, 2000); 
                   timeId = setTimeout(function() {
						_this.parent().parent().parent().parent().parent().hide();
					}, 3000);	
				var quickaddtocart_obj = _this.parent().parent().parent().parent().parent().parent().find('.quickaddtocart');
				var input_num_obj = _this.parent().parent().find('input[name="num"]');
				ga('ec:addProduct', {      
				   'id': quickaddtocart_obj.attr('data_itemno'),					// SKU   
				   'name': quickaddtocart_obj.attr('data_name'),	// 
				   'category': quickaddtocart_obj.attr('ga_categorys'),				// 
				   'brand': 'DL',						// 
				   'price': quickaddtocart_obj.attr('data_price'),				//   
				   'quantity': input_num_obj.val() ? input_num_obj.val():1,				//   
				   'variant':res.variant
				   });   
				ga('ec:setAction', 'add');   
				ga('send', 'event', 'UX', 'click', 'add to cart');     // Send data using an event.
                
			   }

			   else

			   {

				   _this.tip(res.msg, 15, -1, 2000); 

			   }			   

		   }

		}); 

   });

   $('.favorite_btn').live('click',function(){

		var _this = $(this);

		$.ajax({

		   type: "POST",

		   url: "/quickcart.php",

		   data: {quickaddtofavorite:1,id:_this.attr('pid')},

		   dataType: "json",

		   success: function(res){

			   if(res.status)

			   {

				   _this.tip(res.msg, 15, 0, 2000); 

			   }

			   else

			   {

				   _this.tip(res.msg, 15, 0, 2000); 

			   }			   

		   }

		}); 

   });

   $('.quickcart input.cancel_btn').live('click',function(){$(this).parent().parent().parent().parent().parent().hide();});

});

function quickcartsizechange(obj,allstock)

{

	if($(obj).val())

	{

		size = $(obj).val() ;

		stock = $(obj).find('option:selected').attr('stock');

		$(obj).parent().parent().parent().find('.stock').html($(obj).val()+' : '+stock+' Pcs');

	}

	else

	{

		$(obj).parent().parent().parent().find('.stock').html('All '+allstock+' Pcs');

	}

}

</script>

    $('ul.products li').not('.other').hover(

		function(){

		    $(this).find('.quickcart_btn_box').show();

			$(this).addClass('cur');

        $(window).scroll(function() {
            if ($(this).scrollTop() >= 30) {
                $('#top_float').show();
            } else {
                $('#top_float').hide();
            }
        });

        <script language=javascript>
function cshow(id)
{
var obj=document.getElementById(id);
if (obj.style.display=="none")
 {obj.style.display="";}
else
 {obj.style.display="none";}
}
function startlist(root)
{  
	//alert(root.getElementsByTagName("li"));
  var objSon = new Array();
  var objSon = root.getElementsByTagName("li") ;
  for(var i=0;i<=objSon.length-1;i++)
    {
          if(objSon[i].lastChild.nodeName.toLowerCase()=="ul")
	        { 
			  objSon[i].onmouseover=function(){  this.lastChild.style.display='block'; $(this).addClass("aulli1on");}
	          objSon[i].onmouseout=function(){  this.lastChild.style.display='none'; $(this).removeClass("aulli1on"); }
			  //startlist(objSon[i].lastChild);
			}
	}
}

 $(".aulli1").each(function(){
		$(this).hover(
			function(){
				$(this).find(".aliul1").show();
				$(this).addClass("aulli1on");
				},
			function(){
				$(this).find(".aliul1").hide();
				$(this).removeClass("aulli1on");
				}
	    );					
});
</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
$(function(){
	$(".like_sold .like").click(function(){
		var _this = this;
		$.ajax({
		   type: "GET",
		   url: "/index.php?action=add_favorite",
		   data: {pid:$(this).attr('data_id'),ajax:1},
		   dataType: "json",
		   success: function(res){
			 if(res.status)
			 {
				 var old_num = $(_this).text();
				 old_num = old_num.replace("Like(","");
				 old_num = old_num.replace(")","");
				 old_num = parseInt(old_num);
				 old_num = old_num+1;
				 $(_this).text("Like("+old_num+")");
				 $(_this).tip(res.msg, 15, 0, 2000);
			 }
			 else
			 {
				 $(_this).tip(res.msg, 15, 0, 2000);
			 }
		   }
		});
	});
});
function createAjaxLoading()
{
    $('<div/>').appendTo(document.body).addClass('ajax_loading');
}
function removeAjaxLoading()
{
    $('.ajax_loading').remove();
}
</script></div>

<script type="text/javascript">

$(function(){

	$('.quickaddtocart').each(function(){

		$(this).click(function(){

			var _this = $(this);	

			var _parent = $(this).parent().parent();	

			var _quickbox = _parent.find('.quickcart_box');

			if(_quickbox.html()=='')

			{

				_quickbox.show();

				_quickbox.css('position','absolute');

				_quickbox.html('Loading...');

				var size = _this.attr('data');

				result =  eval("("+size+")");

				var carthtml = '<div class="quickcart">   <form>   <input name="id" type="hidden" value="'+_this.attr('pid')+'" />   <input name="quickaddtocart" type="hidden" value="1" />   <ul>';

				carthtml +='        <li>            <div class="property_name">Size : <input name="key0" type="hidden" value="Size" /></div>            <div class="property_value"><select id="style0" name="style0" onchange="quickcartsizechange(this,'+_this.attr('stock')+');"><option value="">Select Size</option>';

                                var total_count = 0;

				for(var key in result)

				{

					result[key] = parseInt(result[key]);	

				    if(result[key]>0)

					{

                                            total_count++;

						if(key=='os')

							size = "one size";

						else

							size = key ;

						carthtml += '<option value="'+size+'" stock="'+result[key]+'">'+size+'</option>';

					}

				}

				carthtml += '</select></div>        </li>';

				carthtml +='        <li>            <div class="property_name">Qty :</div>            <div class="property_value"><input name="num" value="1" /></div>        </li>';

				carthtml +='        <li>            <div class="property_name">Stock :</div>            <div class="property_value"><span class="stock">All '+_this.attr('stock')+' Pcs</span></div>        </li>';

				carthtml +='<li>            <input type="button" value="Submit" class="submit_btn" />            <input type="button" value="Cancel" class="cancel_btn" />        </li>   </ul>   </form></div>';

				_quickbox.html(carthtml);

				_quickbox.css('position','relative');

                                if(total_count==1)

                                {

                                    _quickbox.find('#style0').val(_quickbox.find('#style0').find('option').eq(1).attr('value'));

                                    _quickbox.find('#style0').change();

                                }

			}

			else

			{

				_quickbox.show();

		    }

		});

	});

   $('.quickcart input.submit_btn').live('click',function(){

		var is_submit = true;

		var _this = $(this);

		$(this).parent().parent().parent().find('select').each(function(){

			if(!$(this).val())

			{

				$(this).tip("Please Select " +  $(this).parent().siblings('.property_name').find('input').val(), 15, 0, 2000); 

				is_submit = false;

				return;

			}

		});	

		if(!is_submit)

		{

			return;

		}

		$.ajax({

		   type: "POST",

		   url: "/quickcart.php",

		   data: $(this).parent().parent().parent().serialize(),

		   dataType: "json",

		   success: function(res){

			   if(res.status)

			   {

				   $('#_ajax_div_items').html(res.totalnum);

				   $('._ajax_div_items').html(res.totalnum);

				   _this.tip(res.msg, 15, -1, 2000); 
                   timeId = setTimeout(function() {
						_this.parent().parent().parent().parent().parent().hide();
					}, 3000);	
				var quickaddtocart_obj = _this.parent().parent().parent().parent().parent().parent().find('.quickaddtocart');
				var input_num_obj = _this.parent().parent().find('input[name="num"]');
				ga('ec:addProduct', {      
				   'id': quickaddtocart_obj.attr('data_itemno'),					// SKU   
				   'name': quickaddtocart_obj.attr('data_name'),	// 
				   'category': quickaddtocart_obj.attr('ga_categorys'),				// 
				   'brand': 'DL',						// 
				   'price': quickaddtocart_obj.attr('data_price'),				//   
				   'quantity': input_num_obj.val() ? input_num_obj.val():1,				//   
				   'variant':res.variant
				   });   
				ga('ec:setAction', 'add');   
				ga('send', 'event', 'UX', 'click', 'add to cart');     // Send data using an event.
                
			   }

			   else

			   {

				   _this.tip(res.msg, 15, -1, 2000); 

			   }			   

		   }

		}); 

   });

   $('.favorite_btn').live('click',function(){

		var _this = $(this);

		$.ajax({

		   type: "POST",

		   url: "/quickcart.php",

		   data: {quickaddtofavorite:1,id:_this.attr('pid')},

		   dataType: "json",

		   success: function(res){

			   if(res.status)

			   {

				   _this.tip(res.msg, 15, 0, 2000); 

			   }

			   else

			   {

				   _this.tip(res.msg, 15, 0, 2000); 

			   }			   

		   }

		}); 

   });

   $('.quickcart input.cancel_btn').live('click',function(){$(this).parent().parent().parent().parent().parent().hide();});

});

function quickcartsizechange(obj,allstock)

{

	if($(obj).val())

	{

		size = $(obj).val() ;

		stock = $(obj).find('option:selected').attr('stock');

		$(obj).parent().parent().parent().find('.stock').html($(obj).val()+' : '+stock+' Pcs');

	}

	else

	{

		$(obj).parent().parent().parent().find('.stock').html('All '+allstock+' Pcs');

	}

}

</script>

        <script language=javascript>
function cshow(id)
{
var obj=document.getElementById(id);
if (obj.style.display=="none")
 {obj.style.display="";}
else
 {obj.style.display="none";}
}
function startlist(root)
{  
	//alert(root.getElementsByTagName("li"));
  var objSon = new Array();
  var objSon = root.getElementsByTagName("li") ;
  for(var i=0;i<=objSon.length-1;i++)
    {
          if(objSon[i].lastChild.nodeName.toLowerCase()=="ul")
	        { 
			  objSon[i].onmouseover=function(){  this.lastChild.style.display='block'; $(this).addClass("aulli1on");}
	          objSon[i].onmouseout=function(){  this.lastChild.style.display='none'; $(this).removeClass("aulli1on"); }
			  //startlist(objSon[i].lastChild);
			}
	}
}

 $(".aulli1").each(function(){
		$(this).hover(
			function(){
				$(this).find(".aliul1").show();
				$(this).addClass("aulli1on");
				},
			function(){
				$(this).find(".aliul1").hide();
				$(this).removeClass("aulli1on");
				}
	    );					
});
</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
$(function(){
	$(".like_sold .like").click(function(){
		var _this = this;
		$.ajax({
		   type: "GET",
		   url: "/index.php?action=add_favorite",
		   data: {pid:$(this).attr('data_id'),ajax:1},
		   dataType: "json",
		   success: function(res){
			 if(res.status)
			 {
				 var old_num = $(_this).text();
				 old_num = old_num.replace("Like(","");
				 old_num = old_num.replace(")","");
				 old_num = parseInt(old_num);
				 old_num = old_num+1;
				 $(_this).text("Like("+old_num+")");
				 $(_this).tip(res.msg, 15, 0, 2000);
			 }
			 else
			 {
				 $(_this).tip(res.msg, 15, 0, 2000);
			 }
		   }
		});
	});
});
function createAjaxLoading()
{
    $('<div/>').appendTo(document.body).addClass('ajax_loading');
}
function removeAjaxLoading()
{
    $('.ajax_loading').remove();
}
</script></div>

.zoom2 { border:1px #A6A6A6 solid}

</style><script type="text/javascript" src="/skin/default/pic/jq.puzz.js"></script>

<script type="text/javascript">

$(function(){

	$('.quickaddtocart').each(function(){

		$(this).click(function(){

			var _this = $(this);	

			var _parent = $(this).parent().parent();	

			var _quickbox = _parent.find('.quickcart_box');

			if(_quickbox.html()=='')

			{

				_quickbox.show();

				_quickbox.css('position','absolute');

				_quickbox.html('Loading...');

				var size = _this.attr('data');

				result =  eval("("+size+")");

				var carthtml = '<div class="quickcart">   <form>   <input name="id" type="hidden" value="'+_this.attr('pid')+'" />   <input name="quickaddtocart" type="hidden" value="1" />   <ul>';

				carthtml +='        <li>            <div class="property_name">Size : <input name="key0" type="hidden" value="Size" /></div>            <div class="property_value"><select id="style0" name="style0" onchange="quickcartsizechange(this,'+_this.attr('stock')+');"><option value="">Select Size</option>';

                                var total_count = 0;

				for(var key in result)

				{

					result[key] = parseInt(result[key]);	

				    if(result[key]>0)

					{

                                            total_count++;

						if(key=='os')

							size = "one size";

						else

							size = key ;

						carthtml += '<option value="'+size+'" stock="'+result[key]+'">'+size+'</option>';

					}

				}

				carthtml += '</select></div>        </li>';

				carthtml +='        <li>            <div class="property_name">Qty :</div>            <div class="property_value"><input name="num" value="1" /></div>        </li>';

				carthtml +='        <li>            <div class="property_name">Stock :</div>            <div class="property_value"><span class="stock">All '+_this.attr('stock')+' Pcs</span></div>        </li>';

				carthtml +='<li>            <input type="button" value="Submit" class="submit_btn" />            <input type="button" value="Cancel" class="cancel_btn" />        </li>   </ul>   </form></div>';

				_quickbox.html(carthtml);

				_quickbox.css('position','relative');

                                if(total_count==1)

                                {

                                    _quickbox.find('#style0').val(_quickbox.find('#style0').find('option').eq(1).attr('value'));

                                    _quickbox.find('#style0').change();

                                }

			}

			else

			{

				_quickbox.show();

		    }

		});

	});

   $('.quickcart input.submit_btn').live('click',function(){

		var is_submit = true;

		var _this = $(this);

		$(this).parent().parent().parent().find('select').each(function(){

			if(!$(this).val())

			{

				$(this).tip("Please Select " +  $(this).parent().siblings('.property_name').find('input').val(), 15, 0, 2000); 

				is_submit = false;

				return;

			}

		});	

		if(!is_submit)

		{

			return;

		}

		$.ajax({

		   type: "POST",

		   url: "/quickcart.php",

		   data: $(this).parent().parent().parent().serialize(),

		   dataType: "json",

		   success: function(res){

			   if(res.status)

			   {

				   $('#_ajax_div_items').html(res.totalnum);

				   $('._ajax_div_items').html(res.totalnum);

				   _this.tip(res.msg, 15, -1, 2000); 
                   timeId = setTimeout(function() {
						_this.parent().parent().parent().parent().parent().hide();
					}, 3000);	
				var quickaddtocart_obj = _this.parent().parent().parent().parent().parent().parent().find('.quickaddtocart');
				var input_num_obj = _this.parent().parent().find('input[name="num"]');
				ga('ec:addProduct', {      
				   'id': quickaddtocart_obj.attr('data_itemno'),					// SKU   
				   'name': quickaddtocart_obj.attr('data_name'),	// 
				   'category': quickaddtocart_obj.attr('ga_categorys'),				// 
				   'brand': 'DL',						// 
				   'price': quickaddtocart_obj.attr('data_price'),				//   
				   'quantity': input_num_obj.val() ? input_num_obj.val():1,				//   
				   'variant':res.variant
				   });   
				ga('ec:setAction', 'add');   
				ga('send', 'event', 'UX', 'click', 'add to cart');     // Send data using an event.
                
			   }

			   else

			   {

				   _this.tip(res.msg, 15, -1, 2000); 

			   }			   

		   }

		}); 

   });

   $('.favorite_btn').live('click',function(){

		var _this = $(this);

		$.ajax({

		   type: "POST",

		   url: "/quickcart.php",

		   data: {quickaddtofavorite:1,id:_this.attr('pid')},

		   dataType: "json",

		   success: function(res){

			   if(res.status)

			   {

				   _this.tip(res.msg, 15, 0, 2000); 

			   }

			   else

			   {

				   _this.tip(res.msg, 15, 0, 2000); 

			   }			   

		   }

		}); 

   });

   $('.quickcart input.cancel_btn').live('click',function(){$(this).parent().parent().parent().parent().parent().hide();});

});

function quickcartsizechange(obj,allstock)

{

	if($(obj).val())

	{

		size = $(obj).val() ;

		stock = $(obj).find('option:selected').attr('stock');

		$(obj).parent().parent().parent().find('.stock').html($(obj).val()+' : '+stock+' Pcs');

	}

	else

	{

		$(obj).parent().parent().parent().find('.stock').html('All '+allstock+' Pcs');

	}

}

</script>

                        var search_key = "search keyword or item no";
                        $("#search_keywords").focus(function(){
                            if($(this).val()==search_key)
